Class opencv_dnn.Blob

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bytedeco.javacpp.Pointer

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    Enclosing class:
    opencv_dnn

    @Namespace(value="cv::dnn")
@NoOffset
public static class opencv_dnn.Blob
extends Pointer
    \brief This class provides methods for continuous n-dimensional CPU and GPU array processing. The class is realized as a wrapper over \ref cv::Mat and \ref cv::UMat. It will support methods for switching and logical synchronization between CPU and GPU.
